metadata.name: HAI Surreal Match
metadata.description:
At the heart of “HAI” is the AI Manga, that blends manga & other art styles through the use of AI. "HAI" not only reflects the Japanese word for "yes" or "I understand," but also references "AI" within the title. 'HAI Surreal Match' transports you to a realm where time and universal creativity intertwine, blurring the boundaries between past, present, and future.

Created for the AI Surrealism show in NY, by Exquisite Workers & Superchief Gallery NFT, featuring 100 AI artists, on June 2-8, 2023.
